{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2966,"text":"I'm going to talk a little bit\nabout where technology's going."},{"time":7509,"text":"And often technology comes to us,"},{"time":10566,"text":"we're surprised by what it brings."},{"time":12455,"text":"But there's actually\na large aspect of technology"},{"time":16162,"text":"that's much more predictable,"},{"time":17988,"text":"and that's because technological systems\nof all sorts have leanings,"},{"time":22100,"text":"they have urgencies,"},{"time":23299,"text":"they have tendencies."},{"time":24884,"text":"And those tendencies are derived\nfrom the very nature of the physics,"},{"time":29840,"text":"chemistry of wires\nand switches and electrons,"},{"time":33659,"text":"and they will make reoccurring\npatterns again and again."},{"time":37745,"text":"And so those patterns produce\nthese tendencies, these leanings."}]},{"cues":[{"time":42643,"text":"You can almost think of it\nas sort of like gravity."},{"time":45498,"text":"Imagine raindrops falling into a valley."},{"time":47841,"text":"The actual path of a raindrop\nas it goes down the valley"},{"time":50953,"text":"is unpredictable."},{"time":52651,"text":"We cannot see where it's going,"},{"time":54193,"text":"but the general direction\nis very inevitable:"},{"time":56494,"text":"it's downward."},{"time":58377,"text":"And so these baked-in\ntendencies and urgencies"},{"time":62973,"text":"in technological systems"},{"time":65051,"text":"give us a sense of where things\nare going at the large form."},{"time":69149,"text":"So in a large sense,"},{"time":70574,"text":"I would say that telephones\nwere inevitable,"},{"time":75005,"text":"but the iPhone was not."},{"time":77094,"text":"The Internet was inevitable,"},{"time":79274,"text":"but Twitter was not."}]},{"cues":[{"time":81036,"text":"So we have many ongoing\ntendencies right now,"},{"time":84988,"text":"and I think one of the chief among them"},{"time":87732,"text":"is this tendency to make things\nsmarter and smarter."},{"time":92041,"text":"I call it cognifying -- cognification --"},{"time":94783,"text":"also known as artificial\nintelligence, or AI."},{"time":98025,"text":"And I think that's going to be one\nof the most influential developments"},{"time":101795,"text":"and trends and directions and drives\nin our society in the next 20 years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":108021,"text":"So, of course, it's already here."},{"time":110030,"text":"We already have AI,"},{"time":112258,"text":"and often it works in the background,"},{"time":114680,"text":"in the back offices of hospitals,"},{"time":116290,"text":"where it's used to diagnose X-rays\nbetter than a human doctor."},{"time":121000,"text":"It's in legal offices,"},{"time":122750,"text":"where it's used to go\nthrough legal evidence"},{"time":125142,"text":"better than a human paralawyer."},{"time":127506,"text":"It's used to fly the plane\nthat you came here with."},{"time":132165,"text":"Human pilots only flew it\nseven to eight minutes,"},{"time":134570,"text":"the rest of the time the AI was driving."},{"time":136547,"text":"And of course, in Netflix and Amazon,"},{"time":138744,"text":"it's in the background,\nmaking those recommendations."},{"time":141298,"text":"That's what we have today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":142583,"text":"And we have an example, of course,\nin a more front-facing aspect of it,"},{"time":147408,"text":"with the win of the AlphaGo, who beat\nthe world's greatest Go champion."},{"time":154478,"text":"But it's more than that."},{"time":158555,"text":"If you play a video game,\nyou're playing against an AI."},{"time":161221,"text":"But recently, Google taught their AI"},{"time":165783,"text":"to actually learn how to play video games."},{"time":168686,"text":"Again, teaching video games\nwas already done,"},{"time":171419,"text":"but learning how to play\na video game is another step."},{"time":175340,"text":"That's artificial smartness."},{"time":178571,"text":"What we're doing is taking\nthis artificial smartness"},{"time":183117,"text":"and we're making it smarter and smarter."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186710,"text":"There are three aspects\nto this general trend"},{"time":190629,"text":"that I think are underappreciated;"},{"time":192342,"text":"I think we would understand\nAI a lot better"},{"time":194643,"text":"if we understood these three things."},{"time":196968,"text":"I think these things also would\nhelp us embrace AI,"},{"time":200275,"text":"because it's only by embracing it\nthat we actually can steer it."},{"time":203887,"text":"We can actually steer the specifics\nby embracing the larger trend."}]},{"cues":[{"time":207467,"text":"So let me talk about\nthose three different aspects."},{"time":210470,"text":"The first one is: our own intelligence\nhas a very poor understanding"},{"time":214167,"text":"of what intelligence is."},{"time":216110,"text":"We tend to think of intelligence\nas a single dimension,"},{"time":219787,"text":"that it's kind of like a note\nthat gets louder and louder."},{"time":222561,"text":"It starts like with IQ measurement."},{"time":225192,"text":"It starts with maybe a simple\nlow IQ in a rat or mouse,"},{"time":229308,"text":"and maybe there's more in a chimpanzee,"},{"time":231887,"text":"and then maybe there's more\nin a stupid person,"},{"time":234102,"text":"and then maybe an average\nperson like myself,"},{"time":236222,"text":"and then maybe a genius."},{"time":237536,"text":"And this single IQ intelligence\nis getting greater and greater."},{"time":242516,"text":"That's completely wrong."},{"time":243691,"text":"That's not what intelligence is --\nnot what human intelligence is, anyway."},{"time":247673,"text":"It's much more like a symphony\nof different notes,"},{"time":252203,"text":"and each of these notes is played\non a different instrument of cognition."}]},{"cues":[{"time":255836,"text":"There are many types\nof intelligences in our own minds."},{"time":259561,"text":"We have deductive reasoning,"},{"time":262633,"text":"we have emotional intelligence,"},{"time":264878,"text":"we have spatial intelligence;"},{"time":266295,"text":"we have maybe 100 different types\nthat are all grouped together,"},{"time":270340,"text":"and they vary in different strengths\nwith different people."},{"time":274269,"text":"And of course, if we go to animals,\nthey also have another basket --"},{"time":278819,"text":"another symphony of different\nkinds of intelligences,"},{"time":281384,"text":"and sometimes those same instruments\nare the same that we have."},{"time":284974,"text":"They can think in the same way,\nbut they may have a different arrangement,"},{"time":288559,"text":"and maybe they're higher\nin some cases than humans,"},{"time":291050,"text":"like long-term memory in a squirrel\nis actually phenomenal,"},{"time":293911,"text":"so it can remember\nwhere it buried its nuts."},{"time":296222,"text":"But in other cases they may be lower."}]},{"cues":[{"time":298233,"text":"When we go to make machines,"},{"time":300987,"text":"we're going to engineer\nthem in the same way,"},{"time":303207,"text":"where we'll make some of those types\nof smartness much greater than ours,"},{"time":308241,"text":"and many of them won't be\nanywhere near ours,"},{"time":310836,"text":"because they're not needed."},{"time":312404,"text":"So we're going to take these things,"},{"time":314631,"text":"these artificial clusters,"},{"time":316736,"text":"and we'll be adding more varieties\nof artificial cognition to our AIs."},{"time":322507,"text":"We're going to make them\nvery, very specific."}]},{"cues":[{"time":326602,"text":"So your calculator is smarter\nthan you are in arithmetic already;"},{"time":333168,"text":"your GPS is smarter\nthan you are in spatial navigation;"},{"time":337337,"text":"Google, Bing, are smarter\nthan you are in long-term memory."},{"time":342339,"text":"And we're going to take, again,\nthese kinds of different types of thinking"},{"time":346893,"text":"and we'll put them into, like, a car."},{"time":348850,"text":"The reason why we want to put them\nin a car so the car drives,"},{"time":351931,"text":"is because it's not driving like a human."},{"time":354257,"text":"It's not thinking like us."},{"time":355677,"text":"That's the whole feature of it."},{"time":357621,"text":"It's not being distracted,"},{"time":359180,"text":"it's not worrying about whether\nit left the stove on,"},{"time":361958,"text":"or whether it should have\nmajored in finance."},{"time":364120,"text":"It's just driving."}]},{"cues":[{"time":365297,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":366463,"text":"Just driving, OK?"},{"time":368328,"text":"And we actually might even\ncome to advertise these"},{"time":371289,"text":"as \"consciousness-free.\""},{"time":372858,"text":"They're without consciousness,"},{"time":374656,"text":"they're not concerned about those things,"},{"time":376784,"text":"they're not distracted."}]},{"cues":[{"time":377964,"text":"So in general, what we're trying to do"},{"time":380954,"text":"is make as many different\ntypes of thinking as we can."},{"time":385804,"text":"We're going to populate the space"},{"time":387911,"text":"of all the different possible types,\nor species, of thinking."},{"time":392094,"text":"And there actually may be some problems"},{"time":394186,"text":"that are so difficult\nin business and science"},{"time":397010,"text":"that our own type of human thinking\nmay not be able to solve them alone."},{"time":401076,"text":"We may need a two-step program,"},{"time":403092,"text":"which is to invent new kinds of thinking"},{"time":407692,"text":"that we can work alongside of to solve\nthese really large problems,"},{"time":411450,"text":"say, like dark energy or quantum gravity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":416496,"text":"What we're doing\nis making alien intelligences."},{"time":419166,"text":"You might even think of this\nas, sort of, artificial aliens"},{"time":423259,"text":"in some senses."},{"time":424490,"text":"And they're going to help\nus think different,"},{"time":426814,"text":"because thinking different\nis the engine of creation"},{"time":430470,"text":"and wealth and new economy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":433835,"text":"The second aspect of this\nis that we are going to use AI"},{"time":438782,"text":"to basically make a second\nIndustrial Revolution."},{"time":442135,"text":"The first Industrial Revolution\nwas based on the fact"},{"time":444932,"text":"that we invented something\nI would call artificial power."},{"time":448879,"text":"Previous to that,"},{"time":450053,"text":"during the Agricultural Revolution,"},{"time":452111,"text":"everything that was made\nhad to be made with human muscle"},{"time":455837,"text":"or animal power."},{"time":457565,"text":"That was the only way\nto get anything done."},{"time":459652,"text":"The great innovation during\nthe Industrial Revolution was,"},{"time":462621,"text":"we harnessed steam power, fossil fuels,"},{"time":465754,"text":"to make this artificial power\nthat we could use"},{"time":469634,"text":"to do anything we wanted to do."},{"time":471327,"text":"So today when you drive down the highway,"},{"time":474571,"text":"you are, with a flick of the switch,\ncommanding 250 horses --"},{"time":479120,"text":"250 horsepower --"},{"time":480716,"text":"which we can use to build skyscrapers,\nto build cities, to build roads,"},{"time":485432,"text":"to make factories that would churn out\nlines of chairs or refrigerators"},{"time":491245,"text":"way beyond our own power."},{"time":492923,"text":"And that artificial power can also\nbe distributed on wires on a grid"},{"time":499058,"text":"to every home, factory, farmstead,"},{"time":502281,"text":"and anybody could buy\nthat artificial power,"},{"time":506496,"text":"just by plugging something in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":507992,"text":"So this was a source\nof innovation as well,"},{"time":510455,"text":"because a farmer could take\na manual hand pump,"},{"time":513897,"text":"and they could add this artificial\npower, this electricity,"},{"time":516837,"text":"and he'd have an electric pump."},{"time":518358,"text":"And you multiply that by thousands\nor tens of thousands of times,"},{"time":521700,"text":"and that formula was what brought us\nthe Industrial Revolution."},{"time":524883,"text":"All the things that we see,\nall this progress that we now enjoy,"},{"time":528492,"text":"has come from the fact\nthat we've done that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":530579,"text":"We're going to do\nthe same thing now with AI."},{"time":532951,"text":"We're going to distribute that on a grid,"},{"time":535050,"text":"and now you can take that electric pump."},{"time":537448,"text":"You can add some artificial intelligence,"},{"time":540440,"text":"and now you have a smart pump."},{"time":541945,"text":"And that, multiplied by a million times,"},{"time":543897,"text":"is going to be this second\nIndustrial Revolution."},{"time":546284,"text":"So now the car is going down the highway,"},{"time":548690,"text":"it's 250 horsepower,\nbut in addition, it's 250 minds."},{"time":553008,"text":"That's the auto-driven car."},{"time":554801,"text":"It's like a new commodity;"},{"time":556214,"text":"it's a new utility."},{"time":557541,"text":"The AI is going to flow\nacross the grid -- the cloud --"},{"time":560606,"text":"in the same way electricity did."}]},{"cues":[{"time":562197,"text":"So everything that we had electrified,"},{"time":564601,"text":"we're now going to cognify."},{"time":566693,"text":"And I would suggest, then,"},{"time":568102,"text":"that the formula\nfor the next 10,000 start-ups"},{"time":571858,"text":"is very, very simple,"},{"time":573044,"text":"which is to take x and add AI."},{"time":577100,"text":"That is the formula,\nthat's what we're going to be doing."},{"time":579936,"text":"And that is the way\nin which we're going to make"},{"time":583266,"text":"this second Industrial Revolution."},{"time":585148,"text":"And by the way -- right now, this minute,"},{"time":587326,"text":"you can log on to Google"},{"time":588519,"text":"and you can purchase\nAI for six cents, 100 hits."},{"time":592758,"text":"That's available right now."}]},{"cues":[{"time":594386,"text":"So the third aspect of this"},{"time":597315,"text":"is that when we take this AI\nand embody it,"},{"time":600017,"text":"we get robots."},{"time":601214,"text":"And robots are going to be bots,"},{"time":602941,"text":"they're going to be doing many\nof the tasks that we have already done."},{"time":608357,"text":"A job is just a bunch of tasks,"},{"time":609909,"text":"so they're going to redefine our jobs"},{"time":611695,"text":"because they're going to do\nsome of those tasks."},{"time":613978,"text":"But they're also going to create\nwhole new categories,"},{"time":617199,"text":"a whole new slew of tasks"},{"time":619470,"text":"that we didn't know\nwe wanted to do before."},{"time":621951,"text":"They're going to actually\nengender new kinds of jobs,"},{"time":625612,"text":"new kinds of tasks that we want done,"},{"time":627907,"text":"just as automation made up\na whole bunch of new things"},{"time":631336,"text":"that we didn't know we needed before,"},{"time":633194,"text":"and now we can't live without them."},{"time":635174,"text":"So they're going to produce\neven more jobs than they take away,"},{"time":639154,"text":"but it's important that a lot of the tasks\nthat we're going to give them"},{"time":642612,"text":"are tasks that can be defined\nin terms of efficiency or productivity."},{"time":647676,"text":"If you can specify a task,"},{"time":649528,"text":"either manual or conceptual,"},{"time":651787,"text":"that can be specified in terms\nof efficiency or productivity,"},{"time":656591,"text":"that goes to the bots."},{"time":658758,"text":"Productivity is for robots."},{"time":660960,"text":"What we're really good at\nis basically wasting time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":664054,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":665106,"text":"We're really good at things\nthat are inefficient."},{"time":667446,"text":"Science is inherently inefficient."},{"time":670816,"text":"It runs on that fact that you have\none failure after another."},{"time":673746,"text":"It runs on the fact that you make tests\nand experiments that don't work,"},{"time":677194,"text":"otherwise you're not learning."},{"time":678660,"text":"It runs on the fact"},{"time":679846,"text":"that there is not\na lot of efficiency in it."},{"time":681953,"text":"Innovation by definition is inefficient,"},{"time":684756,"text":"because you make prototypes,"},{"time":686171,"text":"because you try stuff that fails,\nthat doesn't work."},{"time":688902,"text":"Exploration is inherently inefficiency."},{"time":692038,"text":"Art is not efficient."},{"time":693593,"text":"Human relationships are not efficient."},{"time":695744,"text":"These are all the kinds of things\nwe're going to gravitate to,"},{"time":698708,"text":"because they're not efficient."},{"time":700207,"text":"Efficiency is for robots."},{"time":703338,"text":"We're also going to learn\nthat we're going to work with these AIs"},{"time":707485,"text":"because they think differently than us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":710005,"text":"When Deep Blue beat\nthe world's best chess champion,"},{"time":714343,"text":"people thought it was the end of chess."},{"time":716296,"text":"But actually, it turns out that today,\nthe best chess champion in the world"},{"time":720722,"text":"is not an AI."},{"time":722906,"text":"And it's not a human."},{"time":724111,"text":"It's the team of a human and an AI."},{"time":726850,"text":"The best medical diagnostician\nis not a doctor, it's not an AI,"},{"time":730874,"text":"it's the team."},{"time":732074,"text":"We're going to be working with these AIs,"},{"time":734247,"text":"and I think you'll be paid in the future"},{"time":736266,"text":"by how well you work with these bots."},{"time":739026,"text":"So that's the third thing,\nis that they're different,"},{"time":743307,"text":"they're utility"},{"time":744496,"text":"and they are going to be something\nwe work with rather than against."},{"time":748336,"text":"We're working with these\nrather than against them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":750999,"text":"So, the future:"},{"time":752500,"text":"Where does that take us?"},{"time":753944,"text":"I think that 25 years from now,\nthey'll look back"},{"time":757535,"text":"and look at our understanding\nof AI and say,"},{"time":760684,"text":"\"You didn't have AI. In fact,\nyou didn't even have the Internet yet,"},{"time":764008,"text":"compared to what we're going\nto have 25 years from now.\""},{"time":767849,"text":"There are no AI experts right now."},{"time":770920,"text":"There's a lot of money going to it,"},{"time":772643,"text":"there are billions of dollars\nbeing spent on it;"},{"time":774935,"text":"it's a huge business,"},{"time":777123,"text":"but there are no experts, compared\nto what we'll know 20 years from now."},{"time":782064,"text":"So we are just at the beginning\nof the beginning,"},{"time":784973,"text":"we're in the first hour of all this."},{"time":787160,"text":"We're in the first hour of the Internet."},{"time":789119,"text":"We're in the first hour of what's coming."},{"time":791183,"text":"The most popular AI product\nin 20 years from now,"},{"time":795360,"text":"that everybody uses,"},{"time":797499,"text":"has not been invented yet."},{"time":800464,"text":"That means that you're not late."}]},{"cues":[{"time":803684,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":804859,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":805909,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}